<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2012-08-19</DATELINE><TITLE>Facile cleavage of C–C bond: conversion of pyrane derivative to 1,3-oxazin derivative</TITLE><BODY>A cascade reaction that involves a unique C–C bond cleavage has been discovered. This protocol affords an unusual and facile method for the synthesis of 1,3-oxazin derivatives under mild conditions.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>